1.1.0
-----

- New functions
 - PC_PCId(pcpoint|pcpatch)
 - PC_Get(pcpoint) returns float8[]
 - PC_Summary(pcpatch)
- Enhancements
 - Support sigbits encoding for 64bit integers (#61)
 - Warn about truncated values (#68)

